name: Rainbow Road
description: Anyone remember the really pretty but really annoying rainbow road level from the popular Nintendo game Mario Kart?? Well this bracelet is our ode to that wonderful Level of frustration as it was a little bit of a frustration trying to make these although they are really rather pretty and we think that everyone should have one! Packed with 25 charms in rainbow colours what more could we ask for to brighten up our lives what with the seemingly endless grey that Winter brings with it!!

name: Cats Eyes
description:
BitterSweet absolutely love the 50s rockabilly style and when we discovered these gems we just fell in love with there charm! perfect for any lover of 50s nostalgia or any Rockabilly Beauty also perfect for everyone that likes a bit of individuality!

	This necklace is available on a silver 16inch chain.
